org.apache.hadoop.ozone.container.keyvalue

Class KeyValueBlockIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.ozone.container.keyvalue.KeyValueBlockIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.ozone.container.common.interfaces.BlockIterator<org.apache.hadoop.ozone.container.common.helpers.BlockData>

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
public class KeyValueBlockIterator
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.ozone.container.common.interfaces.BlockIterator<org.apache.hadoop.ozone.container.common.helpers.BlockData>
    Block Iterator for KeyValue Container. This block iterator returns blocks which match with the MetadataKeyFilters.KeyPrefixFilter. If no filter is specified, then default filter used is MetadataKeyFilters.getNormalKeyFilter()
